{"tid":1908064,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"立會達半有咩用？","createTime":"2020-03-03T04:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T06:27:41.000Z","uid":272200,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"205f3c30e3114f4640950130a2826a5e9a48cac0","tid":1908064,"uid":272200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:27:05.000Z","msg":"立會達半可以：<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 否決政府包括預算案所有提案，令政府癱瘓，迫使政權和人民談判妥協<br />\n2. 剎停警隊加薪買裝甲車，明日大嶼撥款<br />\n3. 令獻世派議員無法製造流會<br />\n4. 令獻世派議員必須出席每一個會議，否則就可能通過佢地唔想通過的法案<br />\n5. 令民主派議員可以出任包括合法會主席的每一個小組會議主席，然後用議事規則制裁獻世派議員，如叫保安踢9佢出去<br />\n6. 用立法會名義告9班保皇狗<br />\n</span></span><br />\n重有無？缺點都歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f44f8beb841137ab48205b10c3e3cb872631dc","tid":1908064,"uid":272200,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:28:28.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"fd8815249f1349bba71733898d54db9c4279235e","tid":1908064,"uid":272200,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:28:39.000Z","msg":"兩下"},{"pid":"478389092c6597eecbe3aa57068a754b01edeca0","tid":1908064,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8195c04a5b134e8ba4bb37123c34faa1f74d10b8","tid":1908064,"uid":272200,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"478389092c6597eecbe3aa57068a754b01edeca0","tid":1908064,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:15:54.000Z","msg":"正解！所以立會達半，得到既係立會既控制權同否決權<br />\n呢個係政制上既攬炒，政府無錢使（否決有屎係入面既預算案），立法會無限期拉布（因為主席係自己人），動用特權法查政府，成立獨立調查委員會查警暴，對家少一個人開會就即過"},{"pid":"12f963877e1d7f47bf1ad88361f9279616dc4d39","tid":1908064,"uid":320078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:32:43.000Z","msg":"票係一定要投既"},{"pid":"177740dc1d882d32414ca0d19877ea89da3890a3","tid":1908064,"uid":272200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"推推推推"}]}